  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #f28500;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Content.png\" src=\"/images/c/cc/Content.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> This article or section is a <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stub\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:Stub\">stub</a>. You can help \"A Wiki Of Ice And Fire\" by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?title=Shadow_war&amp;action=edit\">expanding it</a> and/or improving existing text.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Shadow war</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Conflict</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Targaryen_campaign_in_Slaver%27s_Bay\" title=\"Targaryen campaign in Slaver&#39;s Bay\">Targaryen campaign in Slaver's Bay</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Date</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/300_AC\" title=\"300 AC\">300&#160;AC</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">Meereen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Result</th><td>\nTemporarily halted, now resumed</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Orchestrator</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/The_Harpy\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"The Harpy\">The Harpy</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Great_Masters\" title=\"Great Masters\">Great Masters</a> (suspects)</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Perpetrator</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Sons_of_the_Harpy\" title=\"Sons of the Harpy\">Sons of the Harpy</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Target</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Freedmen\" title=\"Freedmen\">Freedmen</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Unsullied\" title=\"Unsullied\">Unsullied</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Shavepates\" title=\"Shavepates\">Shavepates</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Brazen_Beasts\" title=\"Brazen Beasts\">Brazen Beasts</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Victims</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Stalwart_Shield\" title=\"Stalwart Shield\">Stalwart Shield</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Rylona_Rhee\" title=\"Rylona Rhee\">Rylona Rhee</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Mossador\" title=\"Mossador\">Mossador</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Duran\" title=\"Duran\">Duran</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>shadow war</b> is the armed resistance of the <a href=\"/index.php/Sons_of_the_Harpy\" title=\"Sons of the Harpy\">Sons of the Harpy</a> against the rule of <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> over <a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">Meereen</a> and the abolition of <a href=\"/index.php/Slavery\" title=\"Slavery\">slavery</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Shadow_war&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A D